---

Third-party dependencies (direct):

  ddgs                    Apache 2.0     DuckDuckGo image search
  requests                Apache 2.0     HTTP client
  beautifulsoup4          MIT            HTML parsing for SEO signal extraction
  Pillow                  HPND / MIT     Image I/O and resampling
  ImageHash               BSD-2-Clause   Perceptual hashing (dedup)
  numpy                   BSD-3-Clause   Vectorized pixel math

Optional (only required by generate.py):

  torch                   BSD-3-Clause   Tensor backbone
  diffusers               Apache 2.0     SDXL pipeline
  transformers            Apache 2.0     CLIP / tokenizers
  accelerate              Apache 2.0     Device dispatch
  safetensors             Apache 2.0     Weight serialization

The default SDXL model used by generate.py is
"stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-base-1.0", licensed under the
CreativeML Open RAIL++-M license:
